    - title: 
      content: 'As they studied the Law, they discovered that the <smallcaps>Lord</smallcaps>
        had commanded through Moses that the Israelites should live in shelters during
        the festival to be held that month.[COMMENT[0]]  '
      comments:
      - number: '8:14 '
