        contents:
        - ft: 'As in some Greek manuscripts (see also 12:3); Hebrew reads '
          body: Meraioth.
    - title: 
      content: "Zechariah was leader of the family of Iddo.\n\tMeshullam was leader
        of the family of Ginnethon.  "
      comments: []
    - title: 
      content: "Zicri was leader of the family of Abijah.\n\tThere was also a[COMMENT[0]]
        leader of the family of Miniamin.\n\tPiltai was leader of the family of Moadiah.  "
      comments:
