    - title: 
      content: 'These were the family leaders of the Levites: Hashabiah, Sherebiah,
        Jeshua, Binnui,[COMMENT[0]] Kadmiel, and other associates, who stood opposite
        them during the ceremonies of praise and thanksgiving, one section responding
        to the other, as commanded by David, the man of God. '
      comments:
